data.description: Welcome home to this loved 4 bed 2.5 bath 2story house in the Sun Meadows neighborhood in south College Station! The first floor primary suite offers an entire wall length of closets and extra wide vanity with double sinks. The three secondary bedrooms are upstairs with one oversized bedroom having two walk-in closets and is a great setup for those that share a bedroom or could make a great upstairs living/game room. The only carpet you'll find in this cozy home is in the primary bedroom and staircase; the entire second floor has laminate wood-look floors. Out back you'll find a stone paver patio and great size backyard. This home is located just a block away from Bachmann Park, Hallaran pool and skate park. Currently zoned for Rock Prairie Elementary, Cypress Grove Intermediate, College Station Middle School, and A&M Consolidated High School.
